would focus on illegal donations made by the conglomerate news 
reports said 
japanese law restricts a company of recruits size to 15 million 
yen 107000 a year in political donations 
takeshita alone has acknowledged receiving more than 130 million 
yen about 1 million from recruit in 198587 
