the battered ancient city where rebels have put communist forces 
under intermittent siege for almost two years 
ana said mujahedeen or islamic holy warriors concentrated 
weekend rocket attacks on kandahars military airport destroying a 
jet bomber a tank two other vehicles and a fuel pumping station 
