independent confirmation 
both sides in the afghan war often make exaggerated and 
contradicting claims and verification is rarely possible 
the sovietbacked peoples democratic party of afghanistan 
seized power in a bloody 1978 coup mujahedeen backed mainly by 
pakistan and the united states are fighting to topple it and 
establish an islamic system of government 
