stefania a real adventure doesnt stop it never ends he 
wrote 
miss follini frowned and watched the screen 
you have lived 130 days in temporary isolation montalbini 
wrote 
miss follini watched the screen stonefaced 
and now the adventure continues montalbini wrote you 
are returning on your trip to eternity 
miss follini continued watching the computer screen 
