the experiment in 30footdeep lost cave in the hills of west 
carlsbad simulated some of the effects of interplanetary space 
travel 
in the absence of clocks and sunlight miss follinis sleepwake 
cycle has been altered radically she tends to stay awake 20 to 25 
hours and sleep about 10 hours 
miss follinis menstrual cycle hasnt helped her guess at the 
passage of time because it stopped in the absence of light days and 
dark nights researcher andrea galvagno said 
miss follini an interior decorator has coped with the 
